Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:30.83,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}茫茫人海行色匆匆　擦肩而过碰撞纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:36.95,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}感受彼此羽翼的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:43.14,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}用寂寞抱紧你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:49.59,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}无须其他任何表示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:52.96,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}等候交融的瞬间　觉醒的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:56.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心急如焚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:02.54,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}时光荏苒转瞬即逝　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:12.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只能叹息　心愿遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:18.31,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}炽热的灵魂　传递真情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:21.51,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不再有保留
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:27.86,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你曾经的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:33.14,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}又在何方…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导航信号接通
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按指示前往四号船坞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计算矢量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认信号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航线修正0.3M106.2D
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,180度调头 开始减速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.61,0:00:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听证会上阿斯兰·萨拉也要出席？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 作为当事人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能作出冷静客观的评判
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布的抗议力度听说不小
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说什么是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.50,0:00:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是关键 阿迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.06,0:00:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧完成梅萨琉斯的修理和补给
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.57,0:01:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次虽说是休假但不会太长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:41.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1180,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}天空之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次确认 半径5000内没有敌人反应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他们已经完全跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔狄弥斯的焰火成了迷惑敌人的障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单就这点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是应该感谢他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.56,0:02:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆脱罗拉西亚级确实是好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们眼下的问题丝毫没有改善
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？一定要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…非说一定不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很难回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 去道个歉比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实就是因为你的一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他遭了很大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他调整人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在很微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之去说一声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则在一条船上多尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬头不见低头见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 赛这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这艘船今后怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前途未卜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 阿尔狄弥斯上也没补给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特还会追来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请允许我们与您同往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉国防委员长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必多礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从未乘上过这艘穿梭机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我也同意你报告里的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题关键 在他们开发出了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此高性能的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员身份无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经删除了相关章节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想您一定会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提及机体驾驶者是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会给保守派留下话柄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不愿听到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的朋友叛逃地球军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的报告内容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们开发出的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然人也可驾驭的高性能机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样 明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要更多的斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为早日结束战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水 水！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够 还要更多水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了 不看看什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点噎死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 限制供水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天人家没冲澡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 强袭维护好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是不能用清洗器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太费力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不经思考就说出那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些话？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔狄弥斯上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说基拉是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说也没说错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后到底打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最佳方案吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有更好的航线了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太靠近地球的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会冲进碎石带
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走这条路线的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实能早进入月球轨道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有可能 突破…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过碎石带？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以这个速度一头扎进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船也会变成碎块儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类进入宇宙以来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有垃圾堆成的垃圾堆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 还不想成为其中…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 碎石带…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化不可能为可能的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一则新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤尼乌斯7号一周年悼念仪式上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莱茵最高议会议长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发表声明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次不幸的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们而言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味着永远不能遗忘的深深伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 她就是你的未婚妻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说拉克丝小姐即将出任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次追悼慰问团的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉委员长和克莱茵议长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两家族的后代相结连理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来是属于你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们当前要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是保护那个未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次召开的是关于
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布联合酋长国所属
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫利奥波利斯被毁一事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时听证会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先请出 劳·鲁·克鲁泽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你的报告开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会提供补给吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说提供…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更接近于就地取材
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正朝碎石带前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎石带？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脑子很快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎石带中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中了宇宙空间中的各种漂流物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 也包括战时被毁的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说 用那个补给？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们也快支撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们到时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶小艇负责一些船外活动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人愿意当捡破烂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但实在没有其他办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想活下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是去打劫死者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是出于需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从他们那里分一些资源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如上所述
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝非攻击赫利奥波利斯本身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那场天崩地裂的灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是源于地球军的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布果然暗地勾结地球军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们违反协约在先
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阿斯哈代表说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他终究也是住在地球上的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 克鲁泽队长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军的那些机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是否值得付出如此牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要截获到手呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于其极具威胁的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将由实际驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并与同型号机体交战过的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉进行详细报告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许阿斯兰·萨拉补充报告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先关于这架名为神盾的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其最大特征…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然造出如此凶恶的杀人工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些自然人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还在试验机阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区5架机动战士 够不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有了原型机 离量产仅一步之遥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道到时候再匆忙应对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些武器充分表明了自然人的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还打算将战火扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位议员 请保持肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人爱好战争
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐意参与杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平 安宁 幸福地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们无非渴望这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是谁践踏了这份向往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是谁 为了一己私欲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们调整人实施压迫和无尽的榨取
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个血色的情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生在尤尼乌斯7号上的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大陆…怎么会在这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤尼乌斯7号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,24万3721人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那场恐怖的悲剧发生一周年之际
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们仍对早期结束战争抱有一丝幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是自然人们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用实际行动回击了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为保护我们的家园而战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果安全必须靠武力去赢取
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只有一战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那里的水？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有将近1亿吨的固态水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 娜塔尔小姐也看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是上万名卫星居民丧命的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是唯一一处水源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人欢呼雀跃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说 找到水啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉戈上尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不想踏入那块地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可没办法啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就意味着 必须活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莱茵议长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么见外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算盼到你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又轮到拉克丝外出公干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能让我看到你们俩在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 麻烦事一桩接一桩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲的说法虽然不无道理…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追击那艘新型舰和机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格尼和博尔顿队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将编入我的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,72小时后出发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们告辞 克莱茵议长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扩大战火有何益处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以更不可轻饶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻碍我们的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:33.10,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}何时起微笑变得如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:45.76,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}一个错误便可将它破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:56.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}将宝贵的东西化作光明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:08.48,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}让它赐予我跨越远方的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:18.79,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}回到流星划落的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:25.63,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}将思念与你分享
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.30,0:18:31.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}感受你在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:44.43,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}拥抱寂寞的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:52.80,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}即便现在天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:58.29,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}一定会相见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:03.69,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}静静的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:10.50,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}拥抱它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:17.38,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,3000)}{\be1\an3}静静的夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}格诺·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为保护我们的家园而战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果安全必须靠武力去赢取
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只有一战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5个小时 应该差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹药补给再有一个来回就可以完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民用船？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是被击落的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强行侦查型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复座Ginn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号如果被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它叫来援军就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 为什么要察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是扎夫特的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为这次死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救生艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算是看出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜欢捡破烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 拉克丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为自然人
